Hypervisor helps to communicate from VM with host computers via a translator application. This translator application is known as supervisor.
Docker works on layer concept.
Docker file: -A file which contains definition, what/how the image will be created.
Docker Image-Using Docker file one image getting created as per our defined definitions in Docker file.
Docker Container-Using docker image, we can start one or multiple containers.
For each line of Docker file; One layer in Docker image is getting created.

